foods.ingredients: CHICKEN INGREDIENTS: CONTAINING UP TO 12% OF A SOLUTION OF WATER, SEASONING (SALT, SPICES, SUGAR, NATURAL FLAVORS, MALTODEXTRIN, CELERY SEED, BUTTERMILK POWDER), RICE STARCH, SODIUM BICARBONATE. BREADED, BATTERED AND PREDUSTED WITH WHEAT FLOUR, WATER, POTATO STARCH, SALT, RICE FLOUR, CORN STARCH, LEAVENING (SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, SODIUM BICARBONATE), YELLOW CORN FLOUR, GARLIC POWDER, SPICES (INCLUDING CELERY SEED), CITRIC ACID, ONION POWDER, SUGAR, ENCAPSULATED CITRIC ACID (CITRIC ACID, PALM OIL), NATURAL FLAVORS, XANTHAN GUM. BREADING SET IN VEGETABLE OIL. SAUCE INGREDIENTS: WATER, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, CORN SYRUP, SUGAR, AGED CAYENNE PEPPER, VINEGAR, SOY SAUCE (WATER, SOYBEANS, WHEAT, SALT, SODIUM BENZOATE), SALT, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, GARLIC, SOYBEAN OIL, SPICES, BEET JUICE (COLOR), XANTHAN GUM.
